{"tid":1181572,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"華為首款折屏機 Mate X 據報或延期發售","createTime":"2019-06-01T17:16:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-02T10:10:40.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"e2a6aabc5238f502aeb631bd2daea5dc5c6f7ac8","tid":1181572,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T17:16:36.000Z","msg":"資訊由 AIMPACT 鋒投 提供 | 2019/05/27 08:49:04<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<br />\nSHARE\t\t<br />\n 在微博上分享<br />\n  AAA<br />\n&lt;匯港通訊&gt; 華為最近接連收到美國供應商、軟件廠商及技術聯盟的限制,包括 ARM、Google(谷歌)等，預計將受到一定影響。<br />\n<br />\n目前,發售最近的就是其首款 5G 折疊屏手機 Mate X,據南韓媒體表示,由於各種不確定因素,該機或將延期。<br />\n<br />\n此前,Google Android(安卓)官網的 5G 終端頁面,將華為 Mate X 作為 5G 代表機型作為展示,但現時已經刪除。據了解,華為 P30 Pro 也從安卓官網撤下,意味 Google 不再提供對上述機型的支持。 (BC)"},{"pid":"458266fc19600863d3edb4004d5d7ec9ecd936fc","tid":1181572,"uid":109923,"like":20,"dislike":4,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T17:21:20.000Z","msg":"技術盜取自三叔，唔延期先係新聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01d9af9267c1ebcc525ac8487c9921e4c4279b98","tid":1181572,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T18:26:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.aimpact.com/article/zho/華為首款折疊屏手機-Mate-X-據報或延期發售-5742230700\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.aimpact.com%2Farticle%2Fzho%2F%E8%8F%AF%E7%82%BA%E9%A6%96%E6%AC%BE%E6%8A%98%E7%96%8A%E5%B1%8F%E6%89%8B%E6%A9%9F-Mate-X-%E6%93%9A%E5%A0%B1%E6%88%96%E5%BB%B6%E6%9C%9F%E7%99%BC%E5%94%AE-5742230700&d=77sZY8L1Q3njiwGc8u9yTnjCBy0DQDxxpn8JrxrWeYE%3D&h=0e6b646f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.aimpact.com/article/zho/華為首款折疊屏手機-Mate-X-據報或延期發售-5742230700</a>"},{"pid":"7b25f1fcaadc7aed8028939a6ca15b59de4c14d1","tid":1181572,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T18:28:00.000Z","msg":"要全部裝返homo系統<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"867375bfb81b1cf6e4e3c09684d3a70facbb3756","tid":1181572,"uid":